  "faq": {
    "items": {
      "zh": [
        {
          "q": "境外保险什么时候买最合适？",
          "a": "建议在确定出行计划后立即投保，尤其是申根签证要求必须持有保险才能递签。提前投保可确保保障覆盖完整行程。"
        },
        {
          "q": "保险覆盖哪些地区？",
          "a": "我们的保险产品覆盖全球200+国家和地区，包括中东、东南亚、欧洲、北美、日韩等。可根据目的地选择对应区域保障方案。"
        },
        {
          "q": "出险后如何理赔？",
          "a": "出险后请及时拨打保险公司紧急救援电话报案。我们的顾问会协助您整理理赔材料、跟进理赔进度，确保快速获赔。"
        },
        {
          "q": "可以保高风险运动吗？",
          "a": "可以。部分保险产品支持附加高风险运动保障，涵盖潜水、滑雪、跳伞、攀岩等活动。请在投保时告知需求。"
        },
        {
          "q": "保险可以用于签证申请吗？",
          "a": "可以。我们提供的保险证明符合申根签证、沙特签证等多国使馆要求，支持中英文/中阿文保单。"
        },
        {
          "q": "保费多少钱？",
          "a": "保费根据目的地、保障天数、保障范围和投保人年龄而定。经济型方案每天低至十几元，顾问会根据您的需求推荐最优性价比方案。"
        }
      ],
      "en": [
        {
          "q": "When is the best time to buy overseas insurance?",
          "a": "We recommend purchasing insurance as soon as your travel plan is confirmed. For Schengen visas, insurance is required before applying."
        },
        {
          "q": "Which regions are covered?",
          "a": "Our insurance covers 200+ countries including Middle East, Southeast Asia, Europe, North America, Japan, and Korea."
        },
        {
          "q": "How do I file a claim?",
          "a": "Call the insurer's emergency hotline immediately. Our advisor will assist with documentation and follow up on your claim."
        },
        {
          "q": "Can I get coverage for extreme sports?",
          "a": "Yes. Some plans offer add-on coverage for high-risk activities like diving, skiing, skydiving, and rock climbing."
        },
        {
          "q": "Can the insurance be used for visa applications?",
          "a": "Yes. Our insurance certificates meet requirements for Schengen, Saudi, and other embassy visa applications, with bilingual policies available."
        },
        {
          "q": "How much does insurance cost?",
          "a": "Premiums depend on destination, duration, coverage scope, and age. Economy plans start from as low as a few dollars per day."
        }
      ]
    }
  },
